{"word":"βιοτεύω","slug":"βιοτεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>βιοτεύω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>From <a href='S:βιοτή'><el>βιοτή</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to live</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to get food</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>: <i>to live by</i> or <i>off</i> a thing, <el>ἀπὸ πολέμου</el> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}